23:15.327 --> 23:17.163
It seems we hit a nerve.

23:17.229 --> 23:20.366
He never took any of this
movie talk seriously.

23:20.467 --> 23:22.635
Townsend's the one
who thought I could act.

23:22.702 --> 23:24.704
Townsend's the one who
tried to make it happen.

23:24.771 --> 23:26.939
Townsend had his own
interests at heart.

23:28.908 --> 23:31.010
