23:44.290 --> 23:46.493
He'd be lost without you.

23:47.560 --> 23:48.995
That's not fair.

23:50.497 --> 23:52.198
Isn't that what you
signed up for?

24:30.302 --> 24:31.571
Scott.

24:42.014 --> 24:43.650
I'm sorry.

24:46.418 --> 24:48.688
I messed everything up.

